      "date": "2013-04-26 06:24:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/839e77c6-ae35-11e2-a8d0-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
